    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(Methionyl sh-Oligopeptide-194 Methionyl sh-Polypeptide-170) is a single chain recombinant peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sh-Oligopeptide-194, Methionine, and sh-Polypeptide-170. The fusion peptide contains 103 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
